      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must cover the full COU geometry, flow regime, and patient population envelope at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic pump geometry rather than the specific VAD impeller geometry; flow regime coverage is partial. Relevance gap of two gradations at MRL 5."
