      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for turbulence model selection, hemolysis damage accumulation law, and non-Newtonian rheology model must be provided with sensitivity analysis at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for the hemolysis power-law damage model has not been systematically evaluated. Sensitivity to turbulence model choice is undocumented. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
