      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters must be characterized with probability distributions and propagated through Monte Carlo UQ at Gradation 5.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but only four of eleven identified uncertain input parameters were assigned distributions; remaining parameters treated as deterministic. Partially assessed; formal status is not-assessed."
