      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of experimental sample variability including batch-to-batch blood analogue variation must be documented at Gradation 4.",
      "rationale": "Sample characterization data for blood analogues were not provided with the submission. Factor is an unresolved epistemic gap; not assessed."
